        "\n",
        "## Checking Invariants\n",
        "\n",
        "::: {#fig-checking-invariants .column-margin}\n",
        "\n",
        "{{< video https://youtu.be/7CVlKQ3UjUI class=\"column-margin\" >}}\n",
